        >
          <div class="w-10 h-10 mb-3">
            <svg
              viewBox="0 0 48 48"
              fill="none"
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="w-full h-full"
            >
              <path
                d="M24 4L4 16v16l20 12 20-12V16L24 4z"
                stroke="#222"
                stroke-width="2.5"
                fill="none"></path>
              <path
                d="M24 4v28M4 16l20 12 20-12"
                stroke="#222"
                stroke-width="2"
                stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-base text-black mb-1">
            Fabricada con acero calibre 16 y paneles aislados
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-500">
            Ofrecemos durabilidad y aislamiento térmico, garantizando resistencia estructural mientras mantiene un ambiente interior controlado.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article
          class="max-w-[300px] shrink-0 bg-white rounded-md p-4 shadow-md
                        transition-all duration-200 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl"
        >
          <div class="w-10 h-10 mb-3">
            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 45 45" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><g id="SVGRepo_bgCarrier" stroke-width="0"></g><g id="SVGRepo_tracerCarrier" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></g><g id="SVGRepo_iconCarrier"> <path d="M23.0261 7.548V11.578L27.0521 9.253L28.0521 10.986L23.0261 13.887V20.815L29.0261 17.351V11.548H31.0261V16.196L34.5171 14.182L35.5171 15.914L32.0261 17.929L36.0521 20.253L35.0521 21.986L30.0261 19.083L24.0261 22.547L30.0271 26.012L35.0521 23.11L36.0521 24.842L32.0261 27.166L35.5171 29.182L34.5171 30.914L31.0261 28.899V33.548H29.0261V27.744L23.0261 24.279V31.208L28.0521 34.11L27.0521 35.842L23.0261 33.517V37.548H21.0261V33.517L17.0001 35.842L16.0001 34.11L21.0261 31.208V24.279L15.0261 27.743V33.548H13.0261V28.898L9.53606 30.914L8.53606 29.182L12.0251 27.166L8.00006 24.842L9.00006 23.11L14.0251 26.011L20.0251 22.547L14.0261 19.083L9.00006 21.986L8.00006 20.253L12.0261 17.929L8.53606 15.914L9.53606 14.182L13.0261 16.196V11.548H15.0261V17.351L21.0261 20.815V13.887L16.0001 10.986L17.0001 9.253L21.0261 11.578V7.548H23.0261Z" fill="#000000"></path> </g></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-base text-black mb-1">Aire acondicionado</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-500">
            Con aire acondicionado de 1.5 toneladas, para que su equipo opere con mayor comodidad. Sabemos que la productividad y eficiencia de operación están directamente relacionadas con un entorno cómodo de trabajo.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article
          class="max-w-[300px] shrink-0 bg-white rounded-md p-4 shadow-md
                        transition-all duration-200 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl"
        >
          <div class="w-10 h-10 mb-3">
            <svg
              width="40"
              height="40"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              ><g id="SVGRepo_bgCarrier" stroke-width="0"></g><g
                id="SVGRepo_tracerCarrier"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"></g><g id="SVGRepo_iconCarrier">
                <path
                  fill-rule="evenodd"
                  clip-rule="evenodd"
                  d="M12 2.75C6.89137 2.75 2.75 6.89137 2.75 12C2.75 17.1086 6.89137 21.25 12 21.25C17.1086 21.25 21.25 17.1086 21.25 12C21.25 6.89137 17.1086 2.75 12 2.75ZM1.25 12C1.25 6.06294 6.06294 1.25 12 1.25C17.9371 1.25 22.75 6.06294 22.75 12C22.75 17.9371 17.9371 22.75 12 22.75C6.06294 22.75 1.25 17.9371 1.25 12ZM6.80317 11.25H9.35352C9.47932 10.8052 9.71426 10.4062 10.0276 10.0838L8.75225 7.87485C7.7184 8.68992 6.99837 9.88531 6.80317 11.25ZM10.0507 7.1238L11.3262 9.33314C11.5418 9.27884 11.7676 9.25 12 9.25C12.2324 9.25 12.4581 9.27883 12.6737 9.33312L13.9493 7.12378C13.3466 6.88264 12.6888 6.75 12 6.75C11.3112 6.75 10.6534 6.88265 10.0507 7.1238ZM15.2477 7.87481L13.9724 10.0837C14.2857 10.4062 14.5207 10.8052 14.6465 11.25H17.1968C17.0016 9.88529 16.2816 8.68988 15.2477 7.87481ZM17.1968 12.75H14.6465C14.5207 13.1949 14.2857 13.5939 13.9723 13.9163L15.2477 16.1252C16.2816 15.3102 17.0016 14.1147 17.1968 12.75ZM13.9492 16.8762L12.6736 14.6669C12.4581 14.7212 12.2324 14.75 12 14.75C11.7676 14.75 11.5419 14.7212 11.3263 14.6669L10.0507 16.8762C10.6534 17.1174 11.3112 17.25 12 17.25C12.6888 17.25 13.3465 17.1174 13.9492 16.8762ZM8.75229 16.1252L10.0276 13.9163C9.71428 13.5938 9.47933 13.1948 9.35352 12.75H6.80317C6.99837 14.1147 7.71842 15.3101 8.75229 16.1252ZM11.3859 13.089C11.3823 13.0869 11.3787 13.0847 11.375 13.0826C11.3715 13.0806 11.368 13.0786 11.3645 13.0766C10.9967 12.859 10.75 12.4583 10.75 12C10.75 11.5434 10.9949 11.1439 11.3605 10.9258C11.3653 10.9231 11.3702 10.9204 11.375 10.9176C11.3801 10.9146 11.3851 10.9116 11.3902 10.9086C11.5705 10.8076 11.7785 10.75 12 10.75C12.2204 10.75 12.4275 10.8071 12.6073 10.9072C12.6131 10.9107 12.619 10.9142 12.6249 10.9177C12.6306 10.9209 12.6362 10.9241 12.642 10.9272C13.0062 11.1457 13.25 11.5444 13.25 12C13.25 12.4595 13.0021 12.8611 12.6327 13.0783C12.6301 13.0797 12.6276 13.0812 12.625 13.0827C12.6222 13.0843 12.6194 13.0859 12.6166 13.0876C12.4347 13.191 12.2242 13.25 12 13.25C11.7768 13.25 11.5673 13.1915 11.3859 13.089ZM5.25 12C5.25 8.27208 8.27208 5.25 12 5.25C15.7279 5.25 18.75 8.27208 18.75 12C18.75 15.7279 15.7279 18.75 12 18.75C8.27208 18.75 5.25 15.7279 5.25 12Z"
                  fill="#000000"></path>
              </g></svg
            >
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-base text-black mb-1">
            Montable en quinta rueda
          </h3>

          <p class="text-gray-500">
            Diseñada para montarse sobre la quinta rueda de la unidad de tolvas, facilitando su transporte sin costos adicionales y de forma más sencilla.
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>

      <div class="flex justify-end gap-2 mt-4">
        <button
          id="btnPrev"
          aria-label="Anterior"
          class="w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center rounded text-xl text-white leading-none cursor-pointer
                 bg-white/10 border border-white/30
                 transition-colors duration-200 hover:bg-red-600 hover:border-red-600
                 disabled:opacity-35 disabled:cursor-not-allowed"
        >
          &#8249;
        </button>
        <button
          id="btnNext"
          aria-label="Siguiente"
          class="w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center rounded text-xl text-white leading-none cursor-pointer
                 bg-white/10 border border-white/30
                 transition-colors duration-200 hover:bg-red-600 hover:border-red-600
                 disabled:opacity-35 disabled:cursor-not-allowed"
        >
          &#8250;
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <style>
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .flex.min-h-\[280px\] {
        flex-direction: column;
      }
      .basis-\[52\%\] {
        flex-basis: auto;
        height: 200px;
      }
      #carruselTrack > article {
        min-width: calc(85% - 0.5rem);
      }
    }
    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      #carruselTrack > article {
        min-width: 90%;
      }
    }
  </style>
</section>

<script>
  const track = document.getElementById("carruselTrack") as HTMLElement;
  const btnPrev = document.getElementById("btnPrev") as HTMLButtonElement;
  const btnNext = document.getElementById("btnNext") as HTMLButtonElement;

  let currentIndex = 0;

  const getVisibleCount = () => (window.innerWidth < 600 ? 1 : 2);
  const getTotalCards = () => track.children.length;
  const getMaxIndex = () => Math.max(0, getTotalCards() - getVisibleCount());

  function updateCarrusel() {
    const card = track.children[0] as HTMLElement;
    const gap = 10;
    const offset = currentIndex * 345;
    track.style.transform = `translateX(-${offset}px)`;
    btnPrev.disabled = currentIndex === 0;
    btnNext.disabled = currentIndex >= getMaxIndex();
  }

  btnNext.addEventListener("click", () => {
    if (currentIndex < getMaxIndex()) {
      currentIndex++;
      updateCarrusel();
    }
  });
  btnPrev.addEventListener("click", () => {
    if (currentIndex > 0) {
      currentIndex--;
      updateCarrusel();
    }
  });
  window.addEventListener("resize", () => {
    currentIndex = Math.min(currentIndex, getMaxIndex());
    updateCarrusel();
  });

  updateCarrusel();
</script>
